            </div>
            <div class = "col">
              <a href = "/news/"><h4>News section</h4></a>
              <p>Fulfills the requirements for personal or small business sites.</p>
              <p>Each article is stored in MongoDB and rendered with the same template file.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class = "sites-list-container col-xl-10 offset-xl-1">
