              <p>A WYSIWYG editor for the news section. You can create new posts, edit existing ones or even save your drafts.</p>
              <p>The main idea was inserting a textarea or input element inside the HTML tags of the article, inheriting the style of the parent element</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

